'''星場'''指的是一套任意大小的視野內可見的恆星，通常是在一些感興趣的天體，其四周範圍內可見的恆星<ref>[http://hubblesource.stsci.edu/sources/illustrations/constellations/ HubbleSOURCE: Constellation Mythological Forms] 2011-10-20</ref><ref>[http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/kepler/multimedia/images/kepler-field-of-view-photo.html Kepler Mission Star Field] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/kepler/multimedia/images/kepler-field-of-view-photo.html |date=20210309164652 }} 2011-10-20</ref>。例如，環繞在[[參宿四|參宿四]]和[[參宿七|參宿七]]的星場可以被定義為全部或部分的[[獵戶座|獵戶座]]。

